value.0: A strange heat radiates from the body of this felled Elkenbeast.
A worried look marks the face of this young dwarf. He exudes a calm self-confidence, however, as if he is infinitely comfortable with his place in the world.

Crafted from fine dwarven leathers, this light armor is traditonally worn by respected herdkeepers. Its intent is not to protect the wearer in battle but to keep at bay the thorns and thistles of the wild and the occasional bite of an angered animal.
Place this object in any area where you want tracking to occur.  Set Will to the DC of tracking in this area.
